1ataniup tusaqlitit uquᒤttumik ulluqaqtillutit;
2ikajuqtiksamiglu tilisivigilitit itjurngᓁttuviqutiminit,
3tunirrutitittuq tamarngmik iqqaumaligit
4tunisivigilitillu uummativit pijumajanginnik
5quviasungnirngmik nilliajumaaqpugut saalaqarngnirngnik,
6maannali qaujimavunga ataniup uqsuqtiqsimajani ikajurngniarngmagit;
7ilangit tatiqaqput aksalualingnik ikimavingnik,
8ᑍkkuali urruinnaqput urrungaliqlutik;
9piuliqsilaurit ataniiq!
